Game is not running. Any solution?

@ everyone with AppID error
go to where you installed the game and open "skidrow.ini" with notepad. simply make the first line under [Game] look like this.

# Environment Application Id.
AppId = 65842

 the appid there can also be changed to delete all progress on your profile if you want to do that.
also, yes you are meant to replace all files with the ones in the skidrow folder.
